# A phased wave approach minimizes disruption while capturing value early
@type: two_column

@col:
  ## Wave 1: Quick Wins (Months 1–9)
  - Dev/test environments and non-critical workloads
  - Collaboration and productivity SaaS migration
  - Data warehouse modernization (cloud-native DWH)
  - Estimated savings: $12M annually

@col:
  ## Wave 2: Core Platform (Months 10–24)
  - Customer-facing applications and APIs
  - Core transaction processing systems
  - Analytics and ML infrastructure
  - Estimated savings: $45M annually + new capability

@notes: Wave 1 builds organizational capability and confidence. It is not just cost savings — it is learning infrastructure for Wave 2.

